[section#linalg.reqs.val
    [:en] Linear algebra value types
    [:zh_CN] 线性代数值类型
]

[para]
[:en] Throughout [#linalg], the following types are
[+:adj linear algebra[!value types[%value type]]]:
[:zh_CN] [#linalg] 的通篇，以下列类型为[+:adj 线性代数[!值类型]]:
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] the [`value_type] type alias of any input or output [`mdspan]
parameter(s) of any function in [#linalg]; and
[:zh_CN@~] [#linalg] 中任何函数的任何输入或输出 [`mdspan] 形参的 [`value_type]
类型别名；以及
[item]
[:en@~] the [`Scalar] template parameter (if any) of any function or class in
[#linalg].
[:zh_CN@~] [#linalg] 中任何函数或类的 [`Scalar] 模板形参（如果有）。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Linear algebra value types shall model [`:c semiregular].
[:zh_CN] 线性代数值类型应当构成 [`:c semiregular]。

[para]
[:en] A value-initialized object of linear algebra value type
shall act as the additive identity.
[:zh_CN] 值初始化的线性代数值类型对象，应当表现为加法单位元。
